Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Skylab crash lands
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bydv
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 15 Jul 1979
US Skylab crash lands into ocean after Western Australia fears of impact. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.